module.administrative: boolean - Whether the module is administrative
module.branch: string - Git branch tracked by this module
module.name: string - Module name
module.terraform_provider: string - Terraform provider for the module

stacks.administrative: boolean - Whether the stack is administrative
stacks.branch: string - Git branch tracked by this stack
stacks.locked_by: string - User who locked the stack, if any
stacks.name: string - Stack display name
stacks.queued_runs: integer - Number of queued runs for this stack
